OL,3,C'Magic': Globe-trotting butler's lost
OL,4,Cpostcards from 1920s reunited with
OL,5,Cfamily
OL,7,FThe family of a globe-trotting butler,
OL,8,Fwho mingled with royalty, have said it
OL,9,Fwas a stroke of "magic" after they
OL,10,Fwere reunited with postcards he wrote
OL,11,Fin the 1920s.
OL,13,FFrank Hills died in 1962, but spent
OL,14,Fthe majority of his working life as
OL,15,Feither a valet ` a personal attendant
OL,16,F` or a butler for various affluent
OL,17,Fpeople.
