OL,5,Cfamily
OL,7,FAs a valet, he got to visit Egypt
OL,8,Fduring the period that King
OL,9,FTutankhamen's tomb was discovered, in
OL,10,F1922.
OL,12,FA series of eight postcards
OL,13,Fdocumenting his travels while on a
OL,14,Fgrand tour in the 1920s, and addressed
OL,15,Fto his wife and baby daughter, ended
OL,16,Fup at an antiques fair on the Isle of
OL,17,FWight, seemingly lost to time.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/13
