OL,3,C'Magic': Globe-trotting butler's lost
OL,4,Cpostcards from 1920s reunited with
OL,5,Cfamily
OL,7,FHowever, Jim Rayner, 50, who set up a
OL,8,FFacebook group called the Forgotten
OL,9,FMessages Project ` to reunite families
OL,10,Fwith postcards, bought them for #15 as
OL,11,Fpart of a bundle.
OL,13,FAfter tracing Laura Parham, Mr Hills'
OL,14,Fgreat granddaughter, he sent the
OL,15,Fpostcards to the family on December
OL,16,F28, which she described as a "late
OL,17,FChristmas present".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/13
