OL,3,C'Magic': Globe-trotting butler's lost
OL,4,Cpostcards from 1920s reunited with
OL,5,Cfamily
OL,7,FMs Parham, 44, who lives in Stamford,
OL,8,FLincolnshire, said: "It was Christmas
OL,9,FEve and I found a message from Jim
OL,10,Fthat had been sat in my Facebook
OL,11,FMessenger junk messages for six
OL,12,Fmonths, so it was sort of magic that
OL,13,FI'd stumbled across this message.
OL,15,F"Jim gave us lots of information and
OL,16,Fsent the postcards to us, which was
OL,17,Fgreat."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/13
