OL,3,C'Magic': Globe-trotting butler's lost
OL,4,Cpostcards from 1920s reunited with
OL,5,Cfamily
OL,7,FLiz Parham, who is Ms Parham's mother
OL,8,Fand the granddaughter of Mr Hills, has
OL,9,Fstored the postcards in a folder at
OL,10,Fher home in Sonning Common,
OL,11,FOxfordshire.
OL,13,FThe 72-year-old lived with Mr Hills
OL,14,Ffor several years growing up, and said
OL,15,Fhe was "reserved".
OL,17,F"I lived in a family home with with my
OL,18,Fparents, sisters and grandparents and
OL,19,Fso I lived with Frank until he died.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/13
