OL,3,C'Magic': Globe-trotting butler's lost
OL,4,Cpostcards from 1920s reunited with
OL,5,Cfamily
OL,7,F"I believe he died in 1962, mum and
OL,8,Fdad moved into the house in 1949 and I
OL,9,Fwas born in 1952.
OL,11,F"He wasn't a very chatty person, but
OL,12,Fhe would always play with us and would
OL,13,Fbe very kind and I knew that he worked
OL,14,Funder Sir Charles Cust and travelled
OL,15,Fwith him to places like Egypt.
OL,17,F"I suppose because of his job, he was
OL,18,Falways quite quiet and reserved."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/13
