OL,3,C'Magic': Globe-trotting butler's lost
OL,4,Cpostcards from 1920s reunited with
OL,5,Cfamily
OL,7,FThe postcards provided a glimpse into
OL,8,Fsome of the countries toured by Mr
OL,9,FHills including Monte Carlo and Lake
OL,10,FComo in Italy, and included messages
OL,11,Fabout his travels and how much he
OL,12,Fmissed his family.
OL,14,FMs Parham and her mother have visited
OL,15,Fboth these locations, which they said
OL,16,Fhas helped them to feel a deeper
OL,17,Fconnection to their late relative.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/13
