OL,3,C'Magic': Globe-trotting butler's lost
OL,4,Cpostcards from 1920s reunited with
OL,5,Cfamily
OL,7,F"We all like to travel in our family
OL,8,Fand it's almost as if we are linked
OL,9,Fthrough his travels too," Ms Parham
OL,10,Fadded.
OL,12,FMr Rayner, who works as a compliance
OL,13,Fofficer at Cherry Godfrey ` a
OL,14,Ffinancial services company, also sent
OL,15,Fthe family a newspaper clipping about
OL,16,Ftheir late relative.
OL,18,FIt revealed he was something of a hero
OL,19,Fwhen a fire occurred at a home he was
OL,20,Fworking at, while a butler.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/13
