OL,3,C'Magic': Globe-trotting butler's lost
OL,4,Cpostcards from 1920s reunited with
OL,5,Cfamily
OL,7,F"In 1949, he was at Seagry House,
OL,8,Fworking under Lady Cowley and there
OL,9,Fwas a fire at that house and and
OL,10,Funfortunately, she lost her life, but
OL,11,Fhe was a hero," said Mr Rayner.
OL,13,F"He ran back into the burning building
OL,14,Fand saved other people."
OL,16,FMrs Parham said it would have been
OL,17,F"nice" if her grandfather was alive to
OL,18,Fsee the postcards again.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/13
