OL,3,C'Magic': Globe-trotting butler's lost
OL,4,Cpostcards from 1920s reunited with
OL,5,Cfamily
OL,7,F"It would be nice if he got the
OL,8,Faccolade for having done these amazing
OL,9,Fthings as he was always just happy in
OL,10,Fthe background," she added.
OL,12,F"We also have some stag antlers that
OL,13,Fwere given to him by George V, I think
OL,14,Fit was, when he was present on a
OL,15,Fshooting trip in Scotland."
OL,17,FMr Rayner said when he uncovered more
OL,18,Fabout Mr Hills' story, it "blew me
OL,19,Faway".
