OL,5,Cfamily
OL,7,FHe said he ` and other members of his
OL,8,FFacebook group ` were able to figure
OL,9,Fout Mr Hills was the writer of the
OL,10,Fpostcards using census data and his
OL,11,Fmarriage register.
OL,13,F"The detectives (members of the group)
OL,14,Frealised this was turning into quite a
OL,15,Fstory and pulled out all the stops,"
OL,16,Fhe added.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/13
