OL,3,C'Magic': Globe-trotting butler's lost
OL,4,Cpostcards from 1920s reunited with
OL,5,Cfamily
OL,7,F"After some great leads including a
OL,8,Fpossible link to the Mountbattens,
OL,9,Fadmin Denise, one of our star
OL,10,Fdetectives, traced three grandchildren
OL,11,Fthrough an ancestry site and found a
OL,12,Fname that we ran through Facebook and
OL,13,Fit matched the profile of Laura."
OL,15,FHe said it was "really joyful" to be
OL,16,Fpart of the story's happy ending.
OL,18,F"Postcards were the text messages of
OL,19,Ftheir day," he added.
